er\">\r\n<h1 class=\"about_compelling\">A \"virtual classroom\" experience</h1>\r\n<p class=\"about_compelling\" style=\"text-align:center\">From your Student Area Dashboard, you\'ll be able to view analysis and constructive critiques of the assignment work you\'ve submitted, as well as receive timely answers to questions posed to your instructor. You\'ll also be able to carry on lively discussions within your \"classroom\" - exchanging feedback and comments with others on your course. You can even schedule a Skype consultation with your instructor to discuss your progress. </p>\r\n<p class=\"txt_white\" style=\"text-align:center\">As an enrolled TCI student you\'ll receive</p>\r\n<ul class=\"virtual_class clearfix\">\r\n<li><a class=\"thumb\" id=\"lessons\"></a><span class=\"whitetxt_small\">Weekly Lessons</span></li>\r\n<li><a class=\"thumb\" id=\"assignments\"></a><span class=\"whitetxt_small\">Weekly Assignments</span></li>\r\n<li><a class=\"thumb\" id=\"critiques\"></a><span class=\"whitetxt_small\">Weekly Critiques of<br>Your Work</span></li>\r\n<li><a class=\"thumb\" id=\"moneyback\"></a><span class=\"whitetxt_small\">Money Back Guarantee</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row_black_wrapper overflow_fix\">\r\n<div class=\"row_inner overflow_fix grey_border\">\r\n<p class=\"title_red txt_center\">Our half-bearded, mostly human team</p>\r\n<ul class=\"instructor_list clearfix\" id=\"instructor_team\">\r\n<li><p>Owner</p><h2>John Smith</h2><img src=\"http://demo.code5fixer.com/2013/rails/wp-content/themes/thecompellingimage/source/images/instruc1.png\" alt=\"John smith\">\r\n<div class=\"share\"><a class=\"twitter\"></a><a class=\"linked\"></a><a class=\"web\"></a></div></li>\r\n<li><p>Operations</p><h2>Monica</h2><img src=\"http://demo.code5fixer.com/2013/rails/wp-content/themes/thecompellingimage/source/images/instruc2.png\" alt=\"Monica\">\r\n<div class=\"share\"><a class=\"twitter\"></a><a class=\"linked\"></a><a class=\"web\"></a></div></li>\r\n<li><p>Designer</p><h2>Abiraham</h2><img src=\"http://demo.code5fixer.com/2013/rails/wp-content/themes/thecompellingimage/source/images/instruc3.png\" alt=\"Abiraham\">\r\n<div class=\"share\"><a class=\"twitter\"></a><a class=\"linked\"></a><a class=\"web\"></a></div></li>\r\n<li><p>Designer</p><h2>Linda Mathew</h2><img src=\"http://demo.code5fixer.com/2013/rails/wp-content/themes/thecompellingimage/source/images/instruc4.png\" alt=\"Linda Mathew\">\r\n<div class=\"share\"><a class=\"twitter\"></a><a class=\"linked\"></a><a class=\"web\"></a></div></li>\r\n<li><p>Designer</p><h2>James</h2><img src=\"http://demo.code5fixer.com/2013/rails/wp-content/themes/thecompellingimage/source/images/instruc5.png\" alt=\"James\">\r\n<div class=\"share\"><a class=\"twitter\"></a><a class=\"linked\"></a><a class=\"web\"></a></div></li>\r\n<li><img src=\"http://demo.code5fixer.com/2013/rails/wp-content/themes/thecompellingimage/source/images/img_instructyou.jpg\" alt=\"John smith\" style=\"margin-top:15px;\"></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row_black_wrapper overflow_fix\">\r\n<div class=\"row_inner clearfix\">\r\n<h1 class=\"about_compelling\">Still not sure? <span style=\"color:#cccccc\">Give a </span>free <span style=\"color:#cccccc\">introductory lesson and assignment a try</span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"intro_lesson\">Sign up for a no-strings-attached account and we\'ll send you an abbreviated sample lesson - complete with related assignment to go out and try - wherever you live. When you\'ve finished, upload your work to the TCI website and you\'ll receive a timely critique of your photos - all for free!  </p>\r\n<a class=\"signup2\" > Sign Up for Course</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-08-16 17:23:11', '2013-08-16 17:23:11', '', '44', 'http://192.168.1.86/rails/44-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0', '');
